OL,3,CLIDL has unveiled plans to invest half
OL,4,Ca billion pounds in new stores
OL,6,FOne of Northern Irelands largest
OL,7,Fretailers is set to invest half a
OL,8,Fbillion pounds and create a thousand
OL,9,Fnew jobs by 2032.
OL,11,FLidl plans to expand across Northern
OL,12,FIreland by opening 16 new stores over
OL,13,Fthe next 6 years, bringing its total
OL,14,Fhere to 60.
OL,16,FLidl's Regional Managing Director,
OL,17,FGordan Cruikshanks said: "We're
OL,18,Fabsolutely delighted today to announce
OL,19,Four investment plans here for Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
