OL,3,CLIDL has unveiled plans to invest half
OL,4,Ca billion pounds in new stores
OL,6,F"In terms of jobs, we currently employ
OL,7,Falmost 1,500 people in Northern
OL,8,FIreland.
OL,10,F"With the additional stores, that
OL,11,Fwould mean that we could increase that
OL,12,Fby almost 1,000."
OL,14,FHe continued: "Before Christmas, we
OL,15,Fannounced investment of 31 million in
OL,16,Fthe northwest of the province as well.
OL,18,F"So, it won't just be in the Greater
OL,19,FBelfast area; it'll be spread right
OL,20,Facross Northern Ireland.
